# P-Core System Commit Template
# 
# Type(scope): Brief description (50 chars max)
#
# Longer description (wrap at 72 chars)
# - What changed and why
# - Any breaking changes
# - Related issues/PRs
#
# Types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, build, ci, chore
# Scopes: dashboard, auth, organization, school-management, students, api, etc.
#
# Examples:
# feat(dashboard): add analytics charts with real-time data
# fix(auth): resolve session timeout issue in production
# refactor(api): migrate to new Hono client pattern
# docs(readme): update deployment instructions
#
# Breaking changes: Add "BREAKING CHANGE:" in footer
# Close issues: Add "Closes #123" in footer
